## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **ruxolitinib Jakafi 2011** = first FDA JAK1/2 MF — paradigm shift. COMFORT-I + COMFORT-II 가 spleen volume reduction + symptom score 임상 endpoint 정립. cytotoxic-only era 종료. quantum-VQE 의 JAK1/2 ATP pocket 직접 fit.
2. **fedratinib Inrebic 2019** = second JAK2 selective. Wernicke encephalopathy black box 부작용. quantum-VQE 의 JAK2 selective vs JAK1 cross 비교.
3. **pacritinib Vonjo 2022** = third JAK2 + IRAK1. 만성 thrombocytopenia (Plt < 50) niche — ruxolitinib 가 thrombocytopenia 유발 vs pacritinib 가 sparing. quantum-VQE 의 JAK2 + IRAK1 dual pocket fit.
4. **momelotinib Ojjaara 2023** = fourth JAK1 + JAK2 + ACVR1 triple-target. first FDA MF + anemia paradigm. ACVR1 inhibition 이 hepcidin 억제 → iron release → anemia 개선. quantum-VQE 의 ACVR1 pocket 가 luspatercept ActR2B/A 와 mechanism 동일축 cross-link.
5. **pelabresib MorphoSys/Constellation Phase 3 MANIFEST** = first BET BD2 selective Phase 3 in MF + ruxolitinib combo. spleen + symptom + anemia + bone marrow fibrosis 4-endpoint. quantum-VQE 의 BET BD2 selective vs BD1 pocket 구분.
6. **navtemadlin MDM2 Phase 3** = TP53-WT MF — MDM2 binding 차단 → p53 stabilization. quantum-VQE 의 MDM2-p53 PPI scaffold fit.
7. **imetelstat MF research** = LR-MDS 2024 후 MF 적응증 expansion research. lipid-modified 13-mer hTR template ASO. quantum-VQE 의 RNA oligonucleotide 결합 modeling.
8. **luspatercept MF anemia research** = MDS-RS + β-thal 후 MF anemia expansion. ACVR2B-IgG1-Fc ligand trap. quantum-VQE 의 ActR2B/A scaffold cross-MDS + cross-thalassemia.
9. **allogeneic HSCT** = MF 의 유일한 cure. RIC + MAC + DIPSS-plus risk-stratified. JAK inhibitor 가 bridge-to-transplant. cross-bone_marrow_failure + cross-transplant + cross-hsct_gvhd_specific.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, MF specific 임상 의미 한정.

